.TH "edma_get_position" 9 "edma_get_position" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
edma_get_position \- returns the current transfer point
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "dma_addr_t" edma_get_position
.BI "(struct edma_cc *ecc "  ","
.BI "unsigned slot "  ","
.BI "bool dst "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ecc" 12
pointer to edma_cc struct
.IP "slot" 12
parameter RAM slot being examined
.IP "dst" 12
true selects the dest position, false the source
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the position of the current active slot
